hilarious , true and funny anybody who has ever worked in any service industry should and can appreciate this movie ... .as a floor capitan in an above average resturant i would have sworn they filmed it in my establishment at times ... .as i watched - i saw so many people that fit the characters in the movie in my own place ... .as the saying goes on the box - `` never upset anybody who comes in contact with your food ! '' this goes along with what my own father told me when we first came to the usa . people get off your cell phones and watch this hilarious movie